                    <div class="sop-document">
                        <h3>üìã Vendor Purchasing Process</h3>
                        <p>This SOP outlines the standard procedure for purchasing from approved vendors.</p>
                        
                        <h4>1. Purchase Request</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Department head submits purchase request via Google Form</li>
                            <li>Include item description, quantity, estimated cost, and business justification</li>
                            <li>Attach any relevant quotes or specifications</li>
                        </ol>

                        <h4>2. Approval Process</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Purchases under $500: Department manager approval</li>
                            <li>Purchases $500-$5,000: Operations manager approval</li>
                            <li>Purchases over $5,000: CFO approval required</li>
                        </ol>

                        <h4>3. Vendor Selection</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Check approved vendor list in AK Purchasing sheet</li>
                            <li>For new vendors, complete vendor evaluation form</li>
                            <li>Obtain minimum 3 quotes for purchases over $1,000</li>
                        </ol>

                        <h4>4. Purchase Order Creation</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Create PO in QuickBooks with approved details</li>
                            <li>Send PO to vendor via email</li>
                            <li>Update purchasing tracker with PO number and expected delivery date</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>

                    <div class="sop-document">
                        <h3>üìã Inventory Receiving Process</h3>
                        <p>Standard procedure for receiving and processing inventory deliveries.</p>
                        
                        <h4>1. Delivery Receipt</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Verify delivery against purchase order</li>
                            <li>Check for damaged or missing items</li>
                            <li>Sign delivery receipt and note any discrepancies</li>
                        </ol>

                        <h4>2. Quality Check</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Inspect items for quality standards</li>
                            <li>Take photos of any defects</li>
                            <li>Complete quality check form</li>
                        </ol>

                        <h4>3. System Update</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Update Inventory Ahead system with received quantities</li>
                            <li>Update purchasing tracker status to "Received"</li>
                            <li>File all documentation in appropriate folder</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>

